text: Hubert Erang (born 4 March 1931) is a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1952 Summer Olympics and the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Esch-sur-Alzette
